{
  "texts": [
    "Despite the success of our approach, there remain several areas for future development.",
    "One significant avenue for improvement is the further refinement of the Router Agent.",
    "Currently, it relies on predefined regular expressions to route queries, but integrating machine learning models to dynamically adapt and learn from query patterns could increase the precision and flexibility of the system.",
    "Additionally, expanding the system's capability to handle a wider variety of legal documents and domains, beyond contract management, would provide greater scalability and versatility.",
    "Another important direction for future work involves improving the system's interaction with graph-based data."
  ]
}